text: Yuval Ashkenazi (; born 13 February 1992) is an Israeli football player. He plays for Maccabi Haifa. ==Club career== He made his Israeli Premier League debut for Bnei Yehuda Tel Aviv on 23 September 2017 in a game against Hapoel Acre. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Israeli footballers Category:Hapoel Ramat Gan F.C. players Category:Hapoel Azor F.C. players Category:Maccabi Kiryat Malakhi F.C. players Category:Hapoel Kfar Shalem F.C. players Category:Bnei Yehuda Tel Aviv F.C. players Category:Maccabi Haifa F.C. players Category:Israeli Premier League players Category:People from Givatayim Category:Association football midfielders
